required files from TCGA:
    - all cases UUIDs of a cancer type from TCGA
    - all methylation files' UUIDs from TCGA
    - all RNA-seq files' UUIDs from TCGA

Then run the python script as follow:
    python create_UUID_payload.py

which will genereate the payload files and the mapping file. Go the payload_files folder, run the script as follow:
    source download_files.sh <payload file>

The raw data will be downloaded in a .gz format.
